    IF YOU HAVEN'T SEEN SOME OF THE PREVIOUS P.O.V. DISCS THEN
 YOU'LL PROBABLY BE WONDERING WHAT THE PICTURE IS ABOUT.
      WELL I ADMIT IT, I SCREWED UP SKUNK'S MEGA ST AND KILLED
 A TT.       IT WASN'T MY FAULT PEOPLE BOOBY TRAPPED THEIR MACHINES BUT
 I SUPPOSE THEY HAD TO AS I WOULD HAVE WIPED THEIR HARD
 DISCS!!!!           I'VE JUST REALIZED THAT THIS IS THE SECOND MENU
 TO SHOW THE SKUNK, HEY OZ WHAT'S UP    DO YOU LIKE HIM OR WHAT?
         HEY ALISTAIR CRAIG (THE SKUNK) WHEN WILL YOU START
 STOCKING OUR DISCS?  HA-HA-HA-HA-HA       P.O.V.'S LONDON
 RAMPAGE '92!        AS ARNY THE TERMINATOR KEEPS SAYING.... WE'LL BE BACK!
     YES INDEED P.O.V. ARE GOING TO THE 7TH 16 BIT SHOW AT
 WEMBLEY IN JULY 1992 SO GO ORDER YOUR TICKETS NOW.    I MAY
 MAKE SOME NEW SHIRTS FOR THE OCCASION SO EVERYONE WILL NOTICE US.
      IF YOU LOVE US, HATE US, WANT TO CONTACT US OR ARE JUST
 NOSEY THEN MAKE SURE YOU ARE THERE ON THE SATURDAY.
       WOW THIS TUNE IS EXCELLENT, I WANTED TO WRITE A WICKED DEMO THAT
 LOOKED LIKE AN AMIGA ONE USING THIS TUNE BUT I HAVE NEVER FOUND THE TIME SO
 I THOUGHT I'D PUT IT ON A MENU.
         TODAY IS MY BIRTHDAY AND TO CELEBRATE
 I DECIDED TO GET A DECENT CAR AS MY INSURANCE HAS
 GONE DOWN ('CAUSE I'M 25 YEARS OLD).  I AM NOW THE PROUD OWNER
 OF A FORD FIESTA XR2.     I ALSO HAVE A KAWASAKI Z650 MOTORCYCLE
 WHICH WIPES THE FLOOR WITH THE XR2 EXCEPT IN THE RAIN!
     THE CAR IS BRIGHT RED (THE ONLY BOY RACER COLOUR YOU CAN GET), I
 WAS A LITTLE TAKEN BACK BY THE INSURANCE THOUGH, I MEAN 400 POUNDS
 FOR FULLY COMPREHENSIVE INSURANCE FOR 12 MONTHS!        I GOT THE
 GARAGE I BOUGHT THE CAR FROM TO FIT AN ALARM TO HELP STOP
 THE THIEVING JOY RIDERS.   IF ANYONE TRIES TO NICK MY ALLOY WHEELS
 I'M FLATTEN THEM.       THE WORST PART OF HAVING AN XR2 IS THAT I'LL
 WORRY ABOUT IT WHEN I LEAVE IT AND GO SHOPPING OR GOTO THE PUB AS
 THERE ARE MORE THIEVES ABOUT THAN IN ALI BAB-BA'S CAVE.
         
